  "texts": [
    "Out of the 9 bugs, 7 have been confirmed by the developers, and 3 have already been fixed by now (the time of paper submission).",
    "We have requested CVE IDs for the confirmed bugs.We utilized AFLNET and NSFUZZ to detect these 9 vulnerabilities.",
    "Both AFLNET and NSFUZZ were configured with the same subject versions to run an equal duration (i.e., 10 repetitions over 24 hours) as CHATAFL.",
    "However, AFLNET was only able to discover three of them (i.e., bugs #5, #6, and #9), and NSFUZZ was able to discover four of them (i.e., bugs #5, #6, #7, and #9).",
    "In addition, AFLNET and NSFUZZ did not find any additional bugs.To understand the contributions of the LLM guidance, we conducted a more detailed investigation of Bug #1, a heap-use-after-free vulnerability."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}